data.description: Welcome to Boyce Crossing in The quaint Village of Boyce. Va . Boyce is a wonderful and historical area close to The Appalachian Trail, River, wineries and brewery's. Boyce Crossing is just a small neighborhood  that has retained its country feeling. Step on to the porch that will accommodate rockers, chairs and more. The front door is 8 ft. tall and brings you into an entry area with a closet and nice half bath. Walk on through and you'll be pleased to see the large and open kitchen with a large island that adjoins the great room. The view is the woods and they bring nice privacy. Upstairs has a very cozy den with an overlook area, primary bedroom with a barn type hinged door.  The  primary bathroom has a separate tub and the shower walls are ceramic tile. The hall bath and the other bedrooms are a very comfortable size as well..    You will love this spacious and unique home when you visit. Make it your next home. GO TO BOYCE CROSSING HOA FOR HOA DOCS.
